        {
            "_id": "3vD1ZYspj89eq3QA",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Guardbreaker",
            "sort": 1000000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Rayhnne makes a Strike against a creature, then Strides. This Stride doesn't trigger reactions. If she ends this Stride in a difference space adjacent to the same creature, she makes another Strike against it. If both Strikes succeed, the creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] until the start of Rayhnne's next turn. Each attack counts against Rayhnne's multiple attack penalty, but the penalty doesn't increase until she's made both attacks.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": []
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "RF1iP0zmJvlkAY8O",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/TwoActions.webp",
            "name": "Smashing Wave",
            "sort": 1100000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Rayhnne smashes her flails together, creating a localized shock wave. She chooses whether this effect is a @Template[type:emanation|distance:15] or a @Template[type:cone|distance:15]. Each creature in the area takes @Damage[10d6[sonic]|options:area-damage] damage with a @Check[reflex|dc:34|basic] saving throw. A creature that fails its save is also @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Dazzled] for 1 round. A creature that critically fails is also @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Deafened] for 1 minute.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
